headline: Stocks to Watch Wednesday Recap: Strategy, Boeing, Netflix, Paramount
summary: ↘️Boeing (BA): Shares turned lower in afternoon trading after President Trump criticized the defense industry and called for changes. Shares in the aerospace company had been higher earlier in the day after Alaska Air (ALK) said it would buy more than 100 new aircraft from Boeing.
